[To find Iasi, in north eastern Romania, go to http://www.fallingrain.com/world/RO/23/Iasi.html.
It is less than 16 km [about 9 mi] from the Moldova border.

Anthrax is very sporadic in Romania and as a result many livestock cases, whether in cattle or sheep, are associated with human cases. Disease awareness is re-learnt the hard way. - Mod.MHJ]

[Photo of anthrax lip lesions:
http://www.consultantlive.com/image/image_gallery?img_id=1561044&t=1272570126694
